<!-- ─── STORY ─── -->
<section id="story">
  <div class="story-grid">
    <div class="story-left reveal">
      <p class="section-label">The Story</p>
      <h2 class="story-headline">When <em>sins</em> come for your daughter</h2>
      <div class="story-featured-quote">
        "The city didn't sleep anymore. Not because it was alive. Because it was afraid."
      </div>
      <p class="story-text">
        Raghav is a feared crime lord whose empire — built over decades on blood, fire, and silence — begins to crumble when a ghost from his past returns. A son he abandoned. A woman he chose to forget. A reckoning he thought would never arrive.
      </p>
      <p class="story-text">
        Veer, Raghav's son-in-law, is no ordinary man. A former black-ops assassin who burned his past and chose peace — until the past refuses to stay burned. Between them stands Aaradhya: daughter, wife, and the only soul still searching for the truth buried beneath the violence.
      </p>
      <p class="story-text">
        When Aryan — the Phantom — surfaces to dismantle everything Raghav built, a war begins not just between men, but between bloodlines, betrayals, and the desperate need for redemption.
      </p>
      <div class="themes">
        <span class="theme-tag">Father &amp; Son</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Redemption</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Betrayal</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Revenge</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Family</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Identity</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Sacrifice</span>
        <span class="theme-tag">Karma</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-right reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s;">
      <p class="section-label">By The Numbers</p>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">13</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Chapters</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Plus a chilling structural epilogue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">4</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Main Voices</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Raghav, Veer, Aaradhya, Aryan</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Sin</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Crimes unraveling in one night</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">4</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Phases</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Checkmate, war, ashes, and ghost fire</div>
        </div>
      </div>
